welcome_message_body: Welcome to Al Jubayl, where the rich history and stunning natural beauty come together to create a truly unique experience. We invite you to explore our charming city, known for its beautiful beaches, thriving industrial sector, and vibrant culture. Enjoy your stay and make unforgettable memories in Al Jubayl!
